      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SEASTRIKE (11) kicked off his career in good style, leading to score by 1.6 metres at Parkes. Draws on the back row this time but looks to have talent and with even luck can go on with the job. BORN TO ENTERTAIN (5) is stepping out for the first time. By Stay Hungry and hails from the Amanda Turnbull stable. Trialling well so anticipating a bright start to his career. HESINHEAVENNOW (9) opened his career in pleasing fashion a week ago, finishing second at this circuit and distance. Shouldn't spend a penny from this draw and the sprint lane may come in handy. May progress along with WICKEDLY SMOOTH (7) who was just behind HESINHEAVENNOW on debut last start, finishing third at this circuit and distance. Has scope for improvement.",
